  "reference_number": "CAF0021",
  "remarks": "\nSewa Security Services is an involved person under the Central African Republic (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2020 as it is and has been involved in actions and activities which undermine or threaten the peace, stability and security of the Central African Republic. It is and has been involved in such actions and activities (i) itself and (ii) because it is responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, and/or promoting the actions and activities of the broader Wagner Group in Central African Republic. \n",
